{"tid":2175095,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"擊敗雙曼PSG？內媒吹捧恒大簽美斯5大優勢 做埋「恒馳」代言人","createTime":"2020-08-26T09:56:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T10:09:55.000Z","uid":35562,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d5ee5c399666d3a15b1f0a18cb5561cf10600b07","tid":2175095,"uid":35562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T09:56:53.000Z","msg":"美斯入信要求離開巴塞隆拿的消息一出，他的去向馬上成為熱話。雖然外界普遍相信美斯轉投曼城、曼聯，或者是巴黎聖日耳門等富豪球會，但有中國傳媒就聲言，這位阿根廷球王有五成機會登陸中超加盟廣州恒大，還點出恒大有五大優勢簽入美斯，並可以成為該集團新能源概念車的代言人。<br />\n<br />\n儘管新型冠狀病毒源自武漢，但有大陸傳媒報道指，目前全球疫情非常嚴重，唯獨中國最為安全，令「梅西」（美斯）東來落班的機會大增，而綜觀目前中超各隊的財力，就有恒大負擔得起其薪酬。其次，環球經濟受疫情拖累，歐洲球壇籠罩着一片減薪潮，既然美斯已經滿身榮譽，不再需要證明自己，到中超掘金絕對是其最佳選擇。第三就是恒大有孔卡的成功案例，美斯絕對可以到廣州名利雙收。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">第四，近期積極推廣「恒馳」新能源概念車的恒大，正可利用美斯擔任全球代言人，帶來無限商機，相比起來其七億歐元（約64.1億港元）贖身費亦不過是「濕濕碎」</span>，加上中國擁有過億球迷，當中不少「偽球迷」喜歡追星，可能為美斯及恒大帶來大量收入。最後一點是恒大的確需要一名中場指揮官，年紀漸大的美斯來到中超，可以輕鬆取代鄭智。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，美斯要求離開巴塞的消息一出，已廣泛獲得大陸球迷關迷，更有不少網民漏夜改圖，製作他穿上中超球衣的合成照。不過亦有傳媒提出，中國足協明年會繼續推出措施遏止金元足球，內地球迷希望美斯轉戰中超，恐怕亦只是一廂情願。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20200826/3I25VGZ3MRBVFKJZT6PGEXJGNM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailysports&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3LrXtVXBwZrdh4M_if_Ac3yV7Rh5-iIIsnQOr2xnVgQF0_8I7iTMK4kG4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200826%2F3I25VGZ3MRBVFKJZT6PGEXJGNM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailysports%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3LrXtVXBwZrdh4M_if_Ac3yV7Rh5-iIIsnQOr2xnVgQF0_8I7iTMK4kG4&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhattnRRycoFBIefads3zMUO1U%3D&h=e178aca3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200826%2F3I25VGZ3MRBVFKJZT6PGEXJGNM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailysports%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3LrXtVXBwZrdh4M_if_Ac3yV7Rh5-iIIsnQOr2xnVgQF0_8I7iTMK4kG4&h=94290f88\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20200826/3I25VGZ3MRBVFKJZT6PGEXJGNM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailysports&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3LrXtVXBwZrdh4M_if_Ac3yV7Rh5-iIIsnQOr2xnVgQF0_8I7iTMK4kG4</a>"},{"pid":"99ce7b510565fa19f566e9ec28e840381b40a66a","tid":2175095,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T09:57:51.000Z","msg":"用人民幣買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1862af9c99f48d6c41d847444db7a94a0f489585","tid":2175095,"uid":20473,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T09:58:44.000Z","msg":"恆遲恆遲 啱晒散步帝美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65155cddc87bca93b56eba7d549a1d51b486f14","tid":2175095,"uid":76753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:00:03.000Z","msg":"張改圖好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026efa5df3dbfbe7c220c1bca90de792df8fb27c","tid":2175095,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d65155cddc87bca93b56eba7d549a1d51b486f14","tid":2175095,"uid":76753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:00:03.000Z","msg":"張改圖好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:09:55.000Z","msg":"真相黎"}]}